00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:42.560
shipped to a central repository at five sites.

228
00:13:43.590 --> 00:13:47.560
So this is the enrollment curve, and the largest enrollment is in Cohort 1,

229
00:13:47.660 --> 00:13:47.970
which is

230
00:13:49.100 --> 00:13:51.440
a little bit above half of the cohort.

