00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:05.060
we have 2,300 patients. So we have a large group

234
00:14:05.140 --> 00:14:08.520
of mutation carriers that we're following longitudinally,

235
00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:12.780
and even the CIS cohort, we have almost 550 patients.

236
00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:18.400
This is just one snapshot of the weekly data we get, and

